heelchair based on the Image processing techniques (Image Acquisition / Data Processing / Device Controller) to analyze eyeball movements and Smart Controller moves the wheelchair towards desired directions.\r\nSolution can address to the current challenges of the Quadriplegia patients or other disabilities and their care giver or family members by enabling the intelligent platform/monitoring system.\r\nNo Market Player / OEMs working on such concept.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Ravi Shankar Kumar, Susanta Roy, Ajay Kumar P, Arnab Ghosh and Rangaraju Devaraju</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Voices Unheard: Migrant Workers in India</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Description:</b> COVID-19 and lockdown has brought the grim face and sorry state of migrant workers. This is an unorganized sector of over 300M migrant workers in India. Most of them are uninsured, live under unhygienic conditions with no bright future prospect for their next generations.\r\nTheir immense contributions in nation building goes unnoticed. In current crisis of Covid-19 they are the worst sufferers, and many have lost their lives and livelihood. Post Covid-19, situation remains even grim if not addressed effectively.\r\nOur solution, Sanmaan – Powered by AI, addresses the problem holistically, it leverages easy to use App for migrant workers and AI built on it to build a long term, sustainable solution for the welfare of migrant workers and growth plans for their next generations.\r\nOur vision is: AAS (meaning Hope): Apmaan (Affront) se Armaan (Aspiration) aur Sanmaan (Self-esteem) tak</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Santosh Bhawar, Radhika Palanivelu, Manish K More, Maheshwar Ture and Suresh Kumar K</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Theme: Innovate for Business</h3>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Ubiquitous Drug Discovery</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Description:</b> Drug discovery is a time taking and costly endeavor. Getting a perfect molecular match which binds to a disease protein is a challenge.\r\nIn our idea, we go beyond existing approved drugs molecules, to consider all/any other molecules as an input for our novel Generative AI model for recommending new drug molecular structures. We finally check if any of our generated molecules, can potentially bind to any disease target proteins.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Praveen Viswanathan, Dhruv Bajpai, Sowmya Parthasarathi, Abhilash Manu and Rohini Nagare</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Zero Data Breach</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Description:</b> <strong>Zero Data Breach platform can help secure data while monetizing it, without losing the competitive advantage.</strong> 50% of Fortune 500 companies have had some form of a data breach. Our Innovation is to bring Clean Dataroom and secure IP Marketplace through “<strong>Zero Data Breach Platform</strong>”. The platform uses privacy-preserving techniques like homomorphic encryption, secure enclaves, and blockchain to give organizations a secure environment to share their data and algorithms in the e-commerce like marketplace. With both data and IP protected, our innovation enables clients with new revenue streams/business models. For e.g. industries like pharma and healthcare can share data to expedite their drug discovery process.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Sunil Krishnan, Deepak Lalan, Melvin Tomy, Amit Kawad and Priyanka Jain</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Disaster Resilient Telcom Networks</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Description:</b> Wildfires causes major damage to telecom network infrastructure across the globe. The calamity also causes major disruption in communications cutting off large sections of disaster affected people without any communication for several days post the disaster.\r\nOur Innovation provides solutions to tackle two challenges.\r\n1. <strong>Frontier is an early warning system</strong> &amp; intelligent disaster impact analysis system built on IoT, AI and Low Power Wide Area NW (LPWAN).\r\n2. <strong>SurvivorNet – An emergency &amp; rapid communication network</strong> in the disaster affected zone using open source cellular radio base station technology and cognitive radio.\r\nThis provides smart platform solutions to address Telcom &amp; similar network challenges during &amp; after disasters. The solution can focus Innovation at scale.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Ramkumar Sembaiyan, Madan Kumar, Sandeep Rajagopal, Aditya Gupta and Krishna Chaitanya</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Digital Rajamouli 2.0</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\">\r\n\r\n<b>Description:</b> I have a dream where I want to see myself in place of Prabhas and be by the side of my crush in Bahubali.\r\n\r\nDigital Rajamouli enables the users to realize this  dream by allowing them to replace the character they fantasize, leveraging the power of Deep-Faking &amp; Artificial Intelligence.\r\n\r\nDisrupt experience of next Gen audience in multi billion-dollar sectors like Entertainment (OTT- $80bn/Year), Social media ($100+ bn/Year) and even EduTech Platforms (eg: BYJUS is expected to double its subscribers base to 100mn by 2022).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Sree Gautham Alluri, Sravani Polapally, Kavin Upadhyay, Injamuri Praveena and Polamarasetty Nirmal</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Voice Dubbing Model/Software</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Problem Statement:</b> Dubbing industry today is heavily dependent on manual efforts from dubbing artists, script writers leading to high cost and long lead time that too with inadequate quality.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Solution:</b> Our “DubbSmart” - AI based Voice Dubbing Platform uses deep learning algorithms to analyze different aspects (tone , accent and pitch etc.) of original voice and converts it into the desired language retaining the same voice characteristics.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Benefit:</b> The solution can eliminate the huge dependency on script writers and dubbing artists providing multi-times efficiency in time to market, drastic cost reductions and can completely revolutionize the entertainment, media, e-Learning and other industries.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Aayush Raj, Varun Pratap Bhardwaj, Anvita Sharma, Kapil Sahni and Manu Bhargava</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Virtual Storefront Platform : A New (Extended) Reality for Retailers and Brands</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Challenge:</b> With customers now quickly moving to e-commerce platforms, there is a need to revitalize luxury retail brands suffering from low footfall and dwindling sales by giving their loyal customers an immersive customer experience that would go far beyond the real-world physical shopping.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Solution:</b> Virtual Storefront platform uses Virtual Reality to teleport the customer to a desired location say a Miami beach where they can try and buy products like a swim wear and matching accessories along with sharing the shopping experience with their friends who they may not be able to meet in real life, all through the comfort of their homes.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Benefits:</b> This innovation takes a huge leap from classic ecommerce thumbnail listing, widens the product searching horizons through theme-based VR showrooms along with the unique feature of collaboration and relationship building – all aiming towards elevating brands in the digital world and enhancing customer loyalty by giving them an inclusive and creative shopping experience.</div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Rupal Sethi, Sanjeev V. Narsipur, Dhruvil Bavishi, Saikiran Kolluri and Abhishek Sappandi</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grayBox\">\r\n<h4>Data Command Center</h4>\r\n<div class=\"slideTxt\">\r\n<div class=\"borderLine\"><b>Description:</b><strong>Bad Data Quality &amp; In-effective Data Management</strong> for an organization increases IT costs, reduces workforce efficiency and may lead to lost opportunities.\r\nSolution is to create a <strong>Virtual Data Command Center</strong> by combining the power of <strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong> and <strong>3D Data Visualization</strong> to bring a paradigm shift in the way data is currently managed within organizations.\r\nThis helps:\r\n1) Explore <strong>Data &amp; Metadata</strong>\r\n2) Perform <strong>Data Operations</strong>\r\n3) Create a self-serviceable <strong>Data Market Place</strong>\r\nEffectively Managing Data can lead to average <strong>cost savings of 33%,</strong> while boosting revenue by an average of 31%. Consolidation of systems can save up to <strong>25% of IT Costs</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"borderLine noBorder\"><b>Innovators :</b> Prashant Wason, Amit Malhotra, Saikat Jana, Sagar Sanjeev and Ashutosh Pandey</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nCan’t wait for the big reveal on our supreme GTIC 2020 winner? Stay tuned for the verdict.\r\n\r\nWe wish all the teams the best of luck.\r\n\r\n<script>\r\n\t\t$(document).ready(function(e) {\r\n\t\t\t$('.grayBox h4').click(function(){\r\n\t\t\t\t$(this).next().slideToggle();\r\n\t\t\t\t$(this).toggleClass(\"slideActive\");\t\r\n\t\t\t});\r\n\t\t});\r\n\t</script>\r\n\r\n</div>","post_link":"https://in.accenture.com/india/?site=1&blog=548&p=55336","site_url":"https://in.accenture.com/india/","post_thumb":"https://cdn.in.accenture.com/prod/wp-c