automation offerings","post_content_stripped":"Smarter, better, faster—meet the new generation of myWizard! This new and powerful version brings expanded capabilities to help our clients transform their business processes. How? By processing optimization through automation. The myWizard platform serves as an \"app store\" where users can access our new patented solutions and more than 20,000 ready-to-go automation and IT assets. Launched in 2016, myWizard brings together a broad suite of applications to help organizations move easily from piecemeal offerings to a more holistic approach to digitalization. Since then, myWizard has already helped some of Accenture’s 9,000 engagements at 1,500 companies. Expanding capabilities through AI With artificial intelligence (AI) at its core, myWizard programs can learn and understand patterns to perform tasks better. This enables companies to unlock new automation opportunities and continuously drive business efficiency, whether it is for optimizing supply chain operations or keeping IT systems at peak performance.  For instance, myWizard uses AI to automate the monitoring and maintenance of network servers. The platform offers tools that can analyze massive amounts of data and identify potential downtime even before it happens. It can even fix these issues automatically using data-based predictions and decisions – a capability that truly reflects the meaning of intelligent automation. Powering customer experience with automation We also have bots that automate customer support queues. If a company wants to manage support tickets faster, myWizard provides virtual agents or chatbots that can help prioritize and resolve issues in real-time, enabling a targeted remedying of customers' pain points. There are also programs designed for software development which can accelerate the deployment of new product or service offerings at up to eight times the speed.  Accelerating the journey to Cloud Helping a client migrate to the Cloud? m